Package productionapp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Item
    interface for items that defines what an item should be able to do.
    MultimediaControl
    Interface that defines what a movie or multimedia player should be able to do.
    ScreenSpec
    Interface for defining what a screen should be able to do.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Class that contains the logic for the GUI.
    Main
    Class that contains the program entry point and sets up and executes the scenes for the GUI.
    MoviePlayer
    Movie player that is a product that implements the MultimediaController defining what a movie player should do.
    Product
    Abstract product class that defines the fields and methods for producible products.
    ProductionRecord
    Production record that represents a specific product that was produced.
    Screen
    Screen class that represents a screen that can be produced.
    Widget
    Implementation of the abstract product class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ItemType
    Item type enum that represents the different categories of products that can be produced.
    MonitorType
    Enum for the different types of monitors that can be produced.
